{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these were mainly in the smaller towns, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took care on the smaller town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Plus, the border, border patrol-- you understand?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were with the military suits or uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in their hats, they had some feathers and things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were supposed to be the rougher, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then little by little, you know, they emptied-- you know, they emptied-- I think we were a transport just before the last, you know, which take-- took us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us-- they walked us-- you know, there was a big square which was near, right across from the military installations there, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they surrounded us, you know, with our-- they-- I don't recall what they told us what to take.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, but everybody carried something-- you know, suitcases and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then of course they took us to the trains and, and packed us into these cars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, the-- You were saying before about selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Would you tell us--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's not necessarily selection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I mean, they said-- you know, like for instance, different areas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said well, we are right-- we are taking these and these people from this street or from this area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The people from here will be in this and this particular day will be taken, you know, to work camps or whatever they--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I came home from the February.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my, my father wrote me, you know, that I should go up to Budapest, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a certain rabbi there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called him the Belzer Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know if you heard of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- at that particular time, you know, he was smuggled out somehow from Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
